metadata.name: ANDY '23
metadata.description:
ANDY '23

As an artist, I've been inspired by many before me, Andy Warhol, being one of the many.

I wanted to make my own play on his famous 'Campbell's Soup Cans' from '61/'62 and mix it with some of my current culture by adding the twist of Bic lighters instead of cans.

A tribute to not only Andy, but the smokers out there burning one.
